<h2>Installation</h2>

<pre>
$ git clone https://github.com/ucan-lab/mixed-nuts ./example
$ cd example
$ npm install
</pre>

<h2>Git initialize</h2>

<pre>
$ npm run git:init
</pre>

<p>or...</p>

<pre>
$ rm -rf .git
$ git init
$ git add .
$ git commit -m "first commit"
</pre>

<h2>Build</h2>

<h3>Build Normal</h3>

<pre>
$ npm run dev
</pre>

<h3>Build Monitoring and Auto reload</h3>

<pre>
$ npm run watch
$ npm run gulp
</pre>

<h3>Build Production</h3>

<pre>
$ npm run prod
</pre>

<h2>Deploy to Netlify</h2>

<pre>
$ npm run dep
</pre>

<h3>Deploy the first time</h3>
<pre>
$ npm run dep

? No site id specified, create a new site: Yes
? Path to deploy? (current dir): public
</pre>

